                            <comment id="24208" author="xhchen111" created="Wed, 6 Jun 2007 21:54:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;winXP&lt;br/&gt;
Java HotSpot(TM) Client VM (build 1.6.0_01-b06, mixed mode, sharing)&lt;br/&gt;
apache-tomcat-5.5.23 AND resin-pro-3.1.1&lt;br/&gt;
Caused by: org.springframework.beans.factory.NoSuchBeanDefinitionException: No unique bean of type &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;com.xhchen.service.IntfImpl&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; is defined: expected single bean but found 0&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="24209" author="xhchen111" created="Wed, 6 Jun 2007 21:56:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I use spring2.1M2 and spring2.1M3-20070606-124.&lt;br/&gt;
and the error is same.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="24210" author="xhchen111" created="Wed, 6 Jun 2007 22:09:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am so sorry ..&lt;br/&gt;
The attachment has spelling error in file  xhchen-servlet.xml: &quot;com.xhchen.servic&quot; should be&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;com.xhchen.service&quot;.&lt;br/&gt;
I try the code again,  ONLY ERROR in resin-pro-3.1.1,  BUT tomcat-5.5.23 IS OK.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="24226" author="xhchen111" created="Thu, 7 Jun 2007 12:33:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;just copy xalan.jar, xercesImpl.jar, xml-apis.jar from apache to resin/lib directory and put the follow content&lt;br/&gt;
in resin.conf, every thing is OK. &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
---------------------------------&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;!-- xml --&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;system-property javax.xml.parsers.DocumentBuilderFactory= &quot;org.apache.xerces.jaxp.DocumentBuilderFactoryImpl&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;system-property javax.xml.parsers.SAXParserFactory= &quot;org.apache.xerces.jaxp.SAXParserFactoryImpl&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;!--  xslt --&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;system-property javax.xml.transform.TransformerFactory= &quot;org.apache.xalan.processor.TransformerFactoryImpl&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
--------------------------------&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="24481" author="mark.fisher" created="Fri, 22 Jun 2007 08:47:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The &apos;context&apos; namespace-based configuration (annotation-demo and component-scan in this case) require configuration changes for using an XSD-capable parser within Resin as described in their documentation (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.caucho.com/resin-3.0/xml/jaxp.xtp#xerces&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://www.caucho.com/resin-3.0/xml/jaxp.xtp#xerces&lt;/a&gt;) and in the Spring reference (&lt;a href=&quot;http://static.springframework.org/spring/docs/2.0.x/reference/xsd-config.html#xsd-config-integration-resin&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://static.springframework.org/spring/docs/2.0.x/reference/xsd-config.html#xsd-config-integration-resin&lt;/a&gt;). &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also as indicated in a previous comment (thank you!), this can be resolved by including the xerces JAR and adding the following lines to resin.conf:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;system-property javax.xml.parsers.DocumentBuilderFactory= &quot;org.apache.xerces.jaxp.DocumentBuilderFactoryImpl&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;system-property javax.xml.parsers.SAXParserFactory= &quot;org.apache.xerces.jaxp.SAXParserFactoryImpl&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue is being marked as a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2109&quot; title=&quot;XML Schema-based configuration can not use in web server resin3&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-2109&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-2109&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
